2005-04-17  lirc  <lirc@k7>

	* /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/doc/html-source/foot.html, /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/configure.in, /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/NEWS, /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/setup.data:
	0.7.1 release

2005-04-16  venkyr  <venkyr@k7>

	* /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/NEWS: Re: iMON-PAD and iMON-RSC support.

	* /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/configure.in, /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/setup.data:
	Added support for iMON-PAD and iMON-RSC.

	* /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/drivers/lirc_imon/lirc_imon.c:
	Printing incoming IR data (for debugging new models) now controlled by
	conditional compilation.

	* /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/remotes/imon/lircd.conf.imon, /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/remotes/imon/lircd.conf.imon-rsc:
	Created separate config file for IMON RSC remote.  Original file (imon)
	contains configuration for IMON MultiMedian remote.

