	removed unnecessary spinlock:
	lirc_dev prevents calling set_use_inc on a plugin already in use

	* /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/remotes/atiusb/lircd.conf.atiusb:
	added ATI Sapphire Remote Bob II USB

