2003-01-04  lirc  <lirc@k7>

	* /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/ANNOUNCE, /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/daemons/irrecord.c, /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/daemons/ir_remote.c, /cvsroot/lirc/lirc/TODO:
